history.content:
Interested in pursuing venture capital? VCIC is a national venture capital investing competition that exposes undergraduate students to the world of venture capital! You will be able to:

  • Evaluate startup pitches and attend trainings from entrepreneurs

  • Interact and network with Senior VCs

  • Learn how to conduct due diligence and term sheet negotiation

  • Represent Cal with your peers in the regional and national competitions in Spring 2022

Check out http://vcicberkeley.org/undergrad.html for more information! Join our upcoming info-sessions to form teams (5 students per team). Our application will be released soon - fill out the interest form below for updates on upcoming events!

 

Interest Form: https://tinyurl.com/vcic-2022

Info-session & Team Mixer #1: 11/17 @ 8-9 pm (Zoom)

Info-session & Team Mixer #2: 11/30 @ 8-9 pm (Chou N440)

Application Deadline: 12/6 @ 11:59 pm PST
